00:05:14.780 --> 00:05:18.260
And now the trick here is
that you can take this elastic

00:05:18.260 --> 00:05:21.560
and just-- at least with mine--
you can use a pair of scissors,

00:05:21.560 --> 00:05:24.900
or you can just break it.

00:05:24.900 --> 00:05:28.150
And that's going to relax
that whole top section, too.

00:05:28.150 --> 00:05:30.590
So that it almost just looks
like the braid goes right

00:05:30.590 --> 00:05:34.290
into the fishtail, which
is kind of a fun look.

00:05:34.290 --> 00:05:37.998
So you can just
soften that all up.

00:05:37.998 --> 00:05:39.850
And it'll just go right in.

00:05:39.850 --> 00:05:40.590
OK, guys.

00:05:40.590 --> 00:05:41.950
